messages.message:
<!channel> travis/jenkins and all service containers have been upgraded to PY3.7! Please upgrade your local venv's!  I've also sent an email with more info.

```    brew install pyenv
    pyenv install 3.7.3
    pip install virtualenv
    pyenv global 3.7.3
    virtualenv -p $(pyenv which python) ~/instabase/venv3
    source activate ~/instabase/venv3
    cd tools/devtools && make update-python3 ```
